message.body: Hey love!
Hey beautiful! Roo!
Rooroo
When is your next available for lunch? It's gonna be hard with clinic shift and weird class schedule. Could you do Thursday after class or Saturday after clinic sometime? That would be more relaxed.
Mrow
Tomorrow take a walk with me after class?
Definitely! :-)
And then we'll figure out getting together!
Really? A walking date!

That would be the best. Really great. I would really like to spend time with you. Please let's do it for real. I get disappointed when I think something will happen and it doesn't. I know you're busy and important and a Marlboro man though. :)
Meow meow! I'm pleased like a pretty little cat. :)
It will make me happy too! And I'm sorry! I want to spend time with you too!!
Sorry about the delay in writing.....bill's being a pain
Got it! I was just asking what you're sorry for!
Sorry because I really did want to spend time today ....that break was too endless ....
It's ok! Thank you though for being sweet.
Can we try to sit together tomorrow? That threw me off too.
Tara doesn't talk or do eye rolls or exasperated looks.
Have I told you today that I love you and that I'm glad you're in my life! I do and I am
Absolutely! Btw...Helen SUCKS
Yah Helen has a problem I think. lol
Her mother was texting instead of breast feeding
I don't get it.
I mean I don't get her.
PS: omg I am still not home. Such a long ride! 7 more blocks on foot.
She s been meditating like a hot New York city minute .......and like Bob flaws....it's not working on her.....Rolly controls the class thru humor but al
so has a strong hand...she's dictatorial and becomes unlikeable....she teaches out of fear....he out of strength
It was rather unpleasant. And so paranoid too! She didn't seem so crazy before.
I saw Lisa today and feel good about working with her.
Yes....I saw Lisa and talked to her for a while ....she was very encouraging .....
I'm feeling more spontaneous lately which feels good. I hugged Lisa and it was a really sweet hug. I was so out of it during that shiatsu course but am feeling better now.
She knows about the chakras and a lot of the stuff I've read....she (again) told me to chill about acupuncture and just take what I need from it and tha
t she's always felt I'll create a new style of acupuncture that will change it all and she'll be coming to me for treatments .....not true but she's kind
to me
You will make a new system of acupuncture.
I will gladly be one of your repeat patients btw.
I'll be in Doreen 's basement baking muffins
You will! I'll most definitely be one of yours!!! And guess what? COLON 7....it's on your ARM!

Thanks sweet one. I'm not too eager to needle you though. I don't know if its at all safe to needle someone who is so sensitive and so adverse to acupuncture. I don't know what purpose needling you would have for me other than loving you AND getting my sh
Your complete consent is sacred to me.
Let's talk about it....
Ok
I trust you!
Also I do not ever want you to let me use you as a practice pincushion either. You are too delicate and lovely to be my acupuncture doll.
I don't mind being your acupuncture doll! :-)
You're too pretty to be poked at at random. I actually am not confident I could really see what you need. And if you did let me see, I'm not sure I could carry it out myself.
I want to make a sex doll joke but don't really have a good one.
Also I know you want to help build up my believing in myself but its ok if I go slow and there are some things I can't do.
Thank you for saying you love me and am glad I'm in your life.
You can.....and I have do much to learn from you! And I promise not to bruise your beautiful sexy face like mean Bob! :-)
I do love you....
I can what? Make a sex doll joke? Lol
Bruise free would be preferred. :) The skin is so tight on the left side it just can't take much. His needling actually hurts (in a way I like). I think he pumped around for "qi" a little much.
What do you think you have to learn from me? I'm flattered.
I was responding to you seeing what i need.....but you can make a sex doll joke too....I would too but I don't want you being grossed out like when Ryan
linked his arm in yours!
Ryan texted me something I will tell you tomorrow that really disturbed me.
Everything.....you understand so much about this that I don't at all....
Really......not 'first memory' type stuff I hope

I wish I could treat like Laura does in the clinic. She used to do txs where the patient might stop the treatment and ask for everyone to go eat Chinese food. Can you imagine me telling Jason I want to cat paw you for 20 minutes? That would be step one.
No it wasn't as bad as first memory which geez Keith now I am thinking about!!!
I feel like my knowledge is small compared to yours sometimes. I understand cm but you understand the whole solar system.
Lol to Laura .....but I have no doubt you'll surpass Laura in all this!
If Jason can bleed my ankles to make them more cosmetically appealing .....you should certainly be allowed to cat paw me! Why what's step two?
Step two I might sing and meow to you for a really long time. You would like it in the end.
Hmmmmm....you think? Lol
You would hate it but in a joking way that would be good for your heart.
Btw confession ....here's a big step in evolution for me .....I was looking forward to hugging you today!
Letting yourself be seen by me is actually a very cherished gift.
I'm so glad Keith. (About the hug.) You have a nice amount of squish around the edges. Maybe it's bulking phase? I don't like muscles bc they are boring and like rocks.
I won't surpass Laura at all. I will be different from her but hopefully as good. She and I have different skills. She is very skilled at leading/working with a group.
Yes....during bulking phase you just have to eat a lot to gain.....cutting phase started Saturday :-)

You looking forward to hugging me is exactly why treatment one would be cat paws. I'm serious. Maybe we could cat paw you some other time/location. It would involve a great deal if trust for that treatment to take root. But it could be really fun.
You'll be amazing .....
More hugs before Saturday then please!!
I hope so. :)
Please promise me you will never flatter me for the sake of me not falling apart.
Yes.....more hugs and a cat paw trust date ...:-)
I'm strong enough to handle the truth.
Cat paws are sacred, and our intimacy must not be violated it violating.
I don't want to ever hurt Joy. Don't just say I won't.
I would never flatter for that reason....I just like telling you the truth that I believe in my heart
Thank you Keith. I just keep saying it bc I want to make sure I can trust you to not just think I'm fragile and sweet.
What does thst text mean .....the violated it violating
You are fragile......but false flattery would cause you pain in the end and make you more fragile ....I wouldn't hurt you like that

I'm concerned about you having dreams involving me being sexy. I don't want to hurt anyone else (mostly Joy) or cross any lines. I also don't want to draw too much of my sexual power from you. Does that make sense? It makes me feel really good to know I a
I know that I'm fragile. It's part of my strength in a way.
It kinda makes sense....but it'll make more sense when we actually talk...and don't worry
I sure hope you're not seeing me as a Ryan type ....you know what I mean
Ok, that's good then. I can cross lines so I have to be careful.
I don't see you as Ryan but I don't know what to think sometimes. I can explain more tomorrow. I am not used to being pretty to men and I'm fragile, so that can be a scary combination.
Ok.....maybe talking in person will help clarify .....that'll be good :-)
I have alot more to say to you but it's too much to try to text.
Yes in person will be good.
Trying to go to 7am yoga.
Ok.......so we'll start talking in person tomorrow. I haven't offended you in some way, have i.?
So tomorrow after school. Can we sit down somewhere? Maybe with food? I want to really talk to you for a minute. We are always talking in between things in little pieces.
No you have not offended me at all.
Sure....sitting down ...with food!
Don't worry. :)
That would be really great. I'm looking forward to it!
Bed now or I will never make it to yoga
Ok.....you sleep so you can get up for yoga...and I'll give Bill his shower and then meditate
Same same text at the same time! Jinx . Sweet dreams!
That sounds nice. The meditating not the shower. :)
Love to you Keith
Love back to you Monica
I'm excited to see you later Keith.
Sleep good tonight. :)
You too! Thank you for dinner...I am glad we talked! Sweet dreams!
I'm glad too! :)
I want one more hug before you lose those 8 lbs. or was it 7?
Deal ....TWO more hugs
Yah!
I'm reading a New Yorker article about people who breed cars that look like or are descended from wild animals. I think that I would get a toyger. (Toy sized tiger!!!)
But look at it rolling in the sun!
These cats coat 9000-30,000! Go to the won or get a toyger? Toss up. :)
Toyger.!
I knew you would vote for team toyger.
Omg there's a feline genome project....go Science!
Tonite was a good night for us
Yes it was
It's nice to have space and time with you and to be there in person too.
I really do need to go to bed now. Don't forget the dream. :) Love, M
Oh my god a horrifying though. Wasn't Thursday supposed to be Dan and Doreen? What happened to Dan? Is he on Fridays now with Ed? I hope not.....
Though = thought
I'll remember! Nighty night! Love, me
Yah! :)
I hope not! LOL
That would be killer. He's hard but he's no Doreen.
I will be there early and we will be table friends. Nobody puts Keithy on the outside edge of the table!
Please tell me you love Dirty Dancing?
Who doesn't!!! :-)
Yes! This might be why I have man troubles. Patrick Swayze was a dancer but also bashed in car windows, which was both terrifying and hot. :)
And short!
Lol
Hahaha! So true!
I like that Jason is small bc I can throw him around a little. Be his Patrick Swayze!
That, my dear, is your problem!
Hey sweetpea, its me. I guess you are already at the party? I hope it's good and not too painful. I was just calling to say hi. Lets talk tomorrow? Or are you headed to NY?
xoxo
Good morning Keith! Are you awake? Do you want to call me? I've been getting up with the birds this week. :) :)
Good morning again! Are you feeling any better today? I love you. I'm not sure if you're coming to school or not today so I'm calling you now. xoxo
Everything is so weird here at the won. There are NO third years in Saturdays! Just me Mike Suzanne and Zach.
Zach and Mike are MIA so far and Jason. Says he will lock out late people! Ha!
Im definitely going to switch to Saturdays
So it's you and Suzanne?
Have a safe and good ride to NY!
Are there enough people to treat people
My dad feeding some ducks I presume. :) :) ￼

Saturdays are not what I expected. It's only Jason which is fine but somewhat disappointing. Stupid Zach showed up but was basically useless since he still has to observe for 15 more hours before he can treat!!! I was annoyed. Mike went home for Morhers D

There are 4 of us so only 2 patients booked per time slot. If you came we could add a third patient slot maybe. So we had four new patients scheduled but only 3 came. There were three first years observing. Suzanne was terrified, even accepted a hug from

I did well. Held my own with Jason but I cried after my first patient. When I went to Jason to discuss my tx strategy I told Jason I wasn't sure what I wanted to do and started throwing out ideas. He was really rough and I stood up to him. I had 7 or so p
Then later I asked him to sign off on point selection and he said, you don't even know what any of those points do. I picked them all for you.
It was so disheartening. We had a hard time but I think that it will level out now.
If he thinks I'm dumb, can you imagine what he would do to someone like Della or Eddie?

But I still learned alot. I asked for a lecture on how he uses the six great channels and he talked and it was useful. He is very involved and doesn't just sit around eating like Jennifer. He asked me the location of st 44 and then I wasn't sure so he sho
Even if I cry alot, I will be ok. Please come on Saturdays!! It's actually nice to have it so small and simple.
Love you. Call me if you can. :)
Jason is very smart but is an idiot when it comes to compassion. He said its bit his problem if someone doesn't like the truth when he tells them.
It does matter if you are nice to people or not.
Aw the heartbreak of being cut off! Please come be my buddy on Saturdays in clinic if you can. I do like Jason's approach in terms of point selection and diagnosis.
We need to talk about good stuff more! I hate ending with 4,000 Zach-related f-bombs. lol
We keep forgetting to talk about the dream! :(
Hey sweetpea. I'm thinking about you!
I'm missing you today!!!!
Stay in NY my darling. Helen just resigned from teaching our class! Janet sent out an email saying counseling is canceled this week!
